{"tid":2038502,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「集思廣益」佢每次鳩拉條線圍一圍就拉100人，點應對好？","createTime":"2020-05-27T15:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T15:29:41.000Z","uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd3214ba3e76881762b93c0109e2b755635cc32f","tid":2038502,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n濫捕根本無成本可言<br />\n<br />\n亂鳩咁拉左幾百人就可以比人冠以「送頭」去形容濫捕呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n我地係咪應該討論下對改善呢個問題？<br />\n<br />\nE.g.<br />\n<br />\n班狗差唔多係街口想推進嘅時候<br />\n本身聚集嘅人要同旁邊嘅人講轉去其他地方或另一條街<br />\n<br />\n否則佢地一衝埋黎，又比佢地鳩拉100個<br />\n<br />\n好撚傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc9fab3d37a5b3933693b05dbb92d856d260926","tid":2038502,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"自推1下"},{"pid":"99dce09c30119c60adcaa73917e00ff5629cdb1c","tid":2038502,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"斬腳趾既方法既話唯有做完野即走，見狗即走，遠一遠見到佢就散，永遠唔接近佢300米"},{"pid":"a4ddf9e571285c5df8f59f7f28f34fcd7d015078","tid":2038502,"uid":283040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:22:40.000Z","msg":"希望大家隻腳唔好停，唔好成日企定定係到，屌狗都要行住屌，要企都企疏啲。好多次都見到係企企下啲狗就大圍捕"},{"pid":"050c770b3b158f312ac512bff4db39498c1dd895","tid":2038502,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99dce09c30119c60adcaa73917e00ff5629cdb1c","tid":2038502,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"斬腳趾既方法既話唯有做完野即走，見狗即走，遠一遠見到佢就散，永遠唔接近佢300米"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:22:43.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n<br />\n但好多人都想留係到食花生或者睇有咩幫到手<br />\n<br />\n搞到一企係到圍埋 就好易比狗圍"},{"pid":"5ba2d9e555d2d13140d6dd493dadc